<li>Tobin, William "<i><a href="http://www2.phys.canterbury.ac.nz/~wjt23/foucault.html" class="external text" title="http://www2.phys.canterbury.ac.nz/~wjt23/foucault.html" rel="nofollow">The Life and Science of Léon Foucault</a></i>".</li>
